Introduction
    -Rock Paper Scissors is one of the most popular childhood games where two people use their hands to pick a random object between rock, paper or scissors. The choice then determines the winner between them.
    -What if you could play this game alone?

Our task is:
    1. Create a Rock Paper Scissor game.
    2. There is only the player and the computer.
    3. The computer will randomly select from all 3 options.
    4. The winner will be announced.